results.name: a(n) = Number of fixed points of permutation A209861/A209862 in range [2^(n-1),(2^n)-1].
comment: See the conjecture given in A209860. If true, then all the terms from a(2) onward are even. a(0) gives the number of fixed points in range [0,0], i.e. 1.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..24
